    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, essentially indistinguishable from a showroom model. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine, factory-fresh condition with no signs of wear. Every mechanical and electronic component functions perfectly, and the car has been meticulously stored and maintained to the highest standards. Buyers can expect a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
